
**The /initial directory contains the SIMC/DATA comparison after using the initial parameters determined by Werner.
They are as follows:

     spec%e%sig_musc  = 1.0e-6, 1.0e-6                 ! add extra mult scatt. in e Arm      
     spec%p%sig_musc  = 1.0e-6, 1.0e-6                 ! add extra mult scatt in pArm                                    
     spec%e%sig_smear = 1.0e-8, 2.0e-3, 2.0e-3, 0.075                 !add extra smear. in recon eArm (Ytar, xptar(in mr), yptar(in mr), delta(in %))           
     spec%p%sig_smear = 1.0e-8, 2.0e-3, 2.0e-3, 0.075                 !add extra smear. in  recon pArm     


